Create a program for managing vehicle records at a car rental company.
The program should enable:
• adding cars to the database (make, model, year of manufacture, registration number, daily price),
• registering car rentals (car, customer, rental date, number of days),
• editing and deleting car and rental records,
• calculating the cost of a car rental based on the number of days and daily price,
• displaying a list of all cars and their availability,
• displaying a list of all rentals.
The program must have a simple graphical interface with Tkinter.
The program should handle exceptions, e.g., a negative number of rental days, a non-existent car or customer, or an invalid menu selection
